review_blob: Flavorful? The only thing I can taste is the alcohol.  I struggled to make this beer dissapear.  I was attracted to the packaging, and the name because it is popular, but yuck this is a gross beer.

I love this beer.  Not too expensive, and tastes a lot better than most beers in its price range.  Not an overpowering taste, pleasant all around.  Definetly the beer to buy if I was going to a party or for most any occassion.

An almost mediocre aroma gives way to an unpleasantly strong taste.  Too much of this will have you thinking youre drinking coffee.  The aftertaste isnt terrible, but you can probably find a better beer.
beer_name: Lake Superior Sir Duluth Oatmeal Stout
